        "authorId" : "a3f1fdb0-47ad-411e-b63d-af6fc71a1fa6",
        "body" : "Only learned this recently, AppVeyor apparently always runs with a working screen. That said, it is not a big deal to run these tests as these appear to be pure Python packages. Though it should be easy to enable in the feedstock.",
